## How to Use This Rule

**This rule activates when a task is identified as time-critical or emergency.**

**Agents should:**
1. Recognize emergency trigger keywords
2. Apply streamlined requirements clarification
3. Focus on minimal viable fix
4. Complete critical validation only
5. Schedule post-deployment validation
6. Use `hotfix/{description}` branch naming
7. Commit with appropriate prefix (often `fix(scope):` or `hotfix(scope):`)















